<paragraph blockId="2.[151,829,1545,1598]" box="[151,829,1576,1598]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
Type-Species: 
<taxonomicName authority="Spinola, 1837" authorityName="Spinola" authorityYear="1837" box="[300,578,1576,1598]" class="Insecta" family="Veliidae" genus="Velia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="basalis">
<emphasis box="[300,429,1576,1598]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Velia basalis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Spinola" box="[435,578,1576,1598]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" refString="Spinola, M. (1837) Essai sur les Genres d'Insectes Appartenants a l'Ordre des Hemipteres, Lin. ou Rhyngotes, Fab. et a la Section des Heteropteres, Dufour. Chez Yvez Gravier, Genes, 383 pp." type="book" year="1837">
Spinola, 
